sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor KH as Khach hang
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Customer as Customer Service
    participant CustomerDB as Customer DB

    KH->>GW: POST /api/customers/:customerId/points/redeem
    Note over KH,GW: points - so diem muon doi
    GW->>Customer: Forward request - yeu cau auth CUSTOMER

    Customer->>CustomerDB: customer.findById(customerId)
    CustomerDB-->>Customer: customer record

    alt Khach hang khong ton tai
        Customer-->>GW: 404 Not Found
        GW-->>KH: Khach hang khong ton tai
    else So diem doi khong hop le - points <= 0
        Customer-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>KH: So diem khong hop le
    else Khong du diem
        Customer-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>KH: Khong du diem de doi
    else Du diem
        Customer->>CustomerDB: customer.update - loyaltyPoints -= points
        Customer->>CustomerDB: pointLog.create
        Note over Customer,CustomerDB: points - so am, reason=REDEEMED<br/>balanceBefore, balanceAfter

        alt loyaltyPoints < 200 va tier = VIP
            Customer->>CustomerDB: customer.update - tier=REGULAR
            Note over Customer: Ha cap tu VIP xuong REGULAR
        end

        CustomerDB-->>Customer: customer da cap nhat

        Customer-->>GW: 200 OK
        Note over Customer,GW: customerId, pointsRedeemed<br/>remainingPoints, tier
        GW-->>KH: Doi diem thanh cong
    end

